parameters: Investigating the forest of Seiko... helping the cat...
Umi "Be thankful to Mia. She's been watching over you the whole time."
Umi "Mmm... Mia. You only care about him."
Kru "Hahaha, that tickles. You're alright, aren't you? No injuries?"
Kru "Thank you. You've been taking care of me, haven't you?"
Umi "Mia has been here the whole time. Umi only occasionally."
Kru "I see. I'm Kru. Thanks for saving me, Umi."
Kru "To say you did nothing... I'm truly grateful..."
Kru "Yeah! But man, when I fell, I thought I was a goner."
Kru "Right, I should be thankful it was just by chance!"
Umi "This village doesn't let strangers in. You're an exception."
Kru "Is that so... Did Umi speak up for me?"
Umi "Sort of... and sort of not..."

Umi "Everyone in the village is worried... You should show your face to
them."
